BEGIN_PGML

You are playing on the magical trampline, it has some interesting properties. Firstly, the trampline gives energy during impact, meaning, you leave at [`[@A]`] the speed that you come into it with.
Assuming that you leave from the middle of trampline and the net is [`[$B]`][`m`] high and having a [`[$C]`][`m`] radius. 
